<h1>Don't Starve Together</h1>

  <p>My favorite game is Don't Starve Together (DST) because it features <strong>hard</strong> challenges and enemies, it features <em>wonderous</em> characters, and you are able to play with your friends.  If you want more information, click <a href="https://goo.gl/BxtJY2">here</a>.</p>

  </header>

<h2>Table of Contents</h2>

<ol>
  <li><a href= "#How-to-play">How to Play</a></li>
  <li><a href= "#The-characters"> The Characters</a></li>
  <li><a href= "#DST">Things I've Done in DST</a></li>
